<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{فَضَرَبْنَا عَلَى آذَانِهِمْ فِي الْكَهْف سِنِين عددا}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّد:</span> و <span class="c2">(عددا)</span> مَنْصُوب <span class="c2">(ل ١٩٢)</span> عَلَى الْمَصْدَرِ؛<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> تُعَدُّ عَدًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>